{"tid":2281104,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"突發！研究發現接近2成40歲以下男性陽痿","createTime":"2020-11-11T04:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T05:07:51.000Z","uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"78663570cc5cc539bf4f66e1d7de8e2d578aee9d","tid":2281104,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T04:11:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/11/11/63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F11%2F11%2F63.jpg&h=1acffcd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男性下半身想重展雄風，千萬別在網路買藥！台灣男性學醫學會警告，國人性功能障礙（<br />\nＥＤ）有年輕化趨勢，四十歲以下年輕男性發生率五年就增三倍，逾六成ＥＤ患者，三年<br />\n內還可能併發心血管疾病；而有病患上網買藥服用三個月未見效，發現藥品成分竟是澱粉<br />\n，甚至有患者吃偽藥導致數天勃起不退，海綿體險些壞死，呼籲若有性功能問題，儘速就<br />\n醫是唯一方法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/paper/1411813\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fpaper%2F1411813&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVEfsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=8cd1b013\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fpaper%2F1411813&h=dcc12d6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/paper/1411813</a>"},{"pid":"06ca0aa9b6b23f94f13cfc4e5bc5e7b9ddc12069","tid":2281104,"uid":128261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T05:05:06.000Z","msg":"1應該唔算陽痿<br />\n睇自拍AV好多鬼佬硬左條J都係軟淋淋，有啲仲淋到可以摺埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9613c01344f14d78e737c14ec2c611d876a3d31b","tid":2281104,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06ca0aa9b6b23f94f13cfc4e5bc5e7b9ddc12069","tid":2281104,"uid":128261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T05:05:06.000Z","msg":"1應該唔算陽痿<br />\n睇自拍AV好多鬼佬硬左條J都係軟淋淋，有啲仲淋到可以摺埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T05:07:51.000Z","msg":"入唔到隧道等於陽痿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji